撚離地"},{"pid":"b3946e8d64066ee6dd85c19c2a269990df726b13","tid":444012,"uid":130221,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T07:25:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>男人老狗做護士笑撚死人咩<br />\n幫啊伯沖涼抺屎抹尿似乜撚野樣<br />\n做人做到咁，真係一d尊嚴都無</blockquote><br />\nMAX 47K 仲想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢d野咁無尊嚴嘅野無人做<br />\n所以先用錢黎吸引人"},{"pid":"59e43f19ac94e728656166a6c4da9d6c6e5268ac","tid":444012,"uid":15503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T07:34:32.000Z","msg":"講到好似聽無料廢老上司 鳩點你做嘢好有尊嚴&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n點都有班病人同家屬 SIR前SIR後咁叫你，好多時係佢哋求你幫手。<br />\n<br />\n而且九成無OT， [好似係]因爲你個更完咗如果你喺病房出咗事，保險唔包，下更IC費事上身會趕你走"},{"pid":"eed97a9ad2a84a9cda4529d3ae51219027976135","tid":444012,"uid":15503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T07:41:54.000Z","msg":"例如伯伯有尿片係身<br />\n但係佢想用便椅去廁所<br />\n<br />\n不過真心round片仲係護士做既<br />\n根本唔夠HCA幫手<br />\n而且好多case HCA搞唔掂<br />\n如果出事街主就大鑊<br />\n所以通常都係一個護士加個HCA<br />\n清醒病人先一個HCA換"},{"pid":"4a6ed7aca63e92c372472eabe8f8f175bad5cded","tid":444012,"uid":129039,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T07:44:33.000Z","msg":"(人生已完)有案底，唔可以註冊做護士<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/431133/page/12?ref=android\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/431133/page/12?ref=android</a>"},{"pid":"b21add6f5e6c8dba1f7d8d405a53ab4382d027ff","tid":444012,"uid":15503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T08:00:32.000Z","msg":"不過如果巴打想入行真係要諗諗<br />\n行內有兩句好出名<br />\nUC精神 做撚死人<br />\n前世做錯事 今世做護士<br />\n<br />\n瘋狂追更係基本嘢，最慘係身上有好多菌潛伏，你身體差或者老咗就爆出嚟，所以晚年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n做大院病房每分鐘都要打醒十二分精神，基本上係無得你hea,嗰頭一個Spo2 Drop，街尾就血尿。轉頭又一個家屬沖埋嚟問有無幹細胞治療可以做。之前夢見有個病人切奇異果片放喺傷口上面，話屋企人上網睇完咁有用喎。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f7d118cd9a5b3f5aaf1608aa30ef45fc80c75d2","tid":444012,"uid":136252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T12:29:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce96407430389665db6308a209e763df5b07c4d8","tid":444012,"uid":25104,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T13:45:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不過如果巴打想入行真係要諗諗<br />\n行內有兩句好出名<br />\nUC精神 做撚死人<br />\n前世做錯事 今世做護士<br />\n<br />\n瘋狂追更係基本嘢，最慘係身上有好多菌潛伏，你身體差或者老咗就爆出嚟，所以晚年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n做大院病房每分鐘都要打醒十二分精神，基本上係無得你hea,嗰頭一個Spo2 Drop，街尾就血尿。轉頭又一個家屬沖埋嚟問有無幹細胞治療可以做。之前夢見有個病人切奇異果片放喺傷口上面，話屋企人上網睇完咁有用喎。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n那打素精神，做死自己人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b1292410c393ec41a1bbe1f879e8d4f157b8a90","tid":444012,"uid":16284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T13:51:55.000Z","msg":"新仔未夠料果時你預左無咩尊嚴，連做得耐d 既PCA 同文員都會屌鳩你。"},{"pid":"75884df675ba3020553bfbce73ebc34d4dca1b4c","tid":444012,"uid":36951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T02:59:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>新仔未夠料果時你預左無咩尊嚴，連做得耐d 既PCA 同文員都會屌鳩你。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d06b8199beca3994beeb9fd69ba499287cb08995","tid":444012,"uid":78349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T03:18:43.000Z","msg":"( Show Blocked User - 乜撚野屌你 )"},{"pid":"31237705b889